summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning; amending Chapter 23.32 of the Seattle Municipal Code at page 173 of the Official Land Use Map, to rezone property located at 3909 S. Othello Street from Lowrise 4 Residential/Commercial (L4 R/C) to Neighborhood Commercial 3 with a 65' height limit and pedestrian overlay (NC3P-65)'. (Petition by Gay Westmoreland, C.F. 309053, DPD Project 3007863).
